class Solution {
    public int reachNumber(int target) {
        target = Math.abs(target);
        int step = 0;
        int sum = 0;
        while (sum < target || (sum - target) % 2 != 0) {
            step += 1;
            sum += step;
        }
        return step;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(sqrt(target))
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: The solution iteratively increases the step count until the sum of steps is greater than or equal to the target and their difference is even, ensuring the destination can be reached.

